i	/	tilde.team	70
iAs I said, it supports some quirks for specific	/	tilde.team	70
iinstructions, because according to some old documents,fx55,	/	tilde.team	70
ifx65, 8xy6 and 8xye dont have the same semantic depending of	/	tilde.team	70
ithe machine they were implemeneted on.	/	tilde.team	70
i	/	tilde.team	70
